mlops\".\"main_query\".\"read_silver_stock_prices\"\ngroup by 1, 2, 3, 4, 5\n  );\n", "name": "SQLQuery", "pid": 67808, "thread": "Thread-4 (worker)", "ts": "2026-07-19T10:28:18.320733Z"}}
